| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2455 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9c0b1376-5508-52df-be65-e6bee2a5297a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
